## 4. Type Casting

Type casting means converting one data type into another.

### Integer to Float

```python
num = 10
print(float(num))
```

### Float to Integer

```python
num = 10.5
print(int(num))
```

### Integer to String

```python
age = 22
print(str(age))
```

